<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Welcome to BlogPost</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/slider.css">
    <style>
        .slider .slide:nth-child(1) {
            background: url("/images/slider-1.jpeg") no-repeat center center/cover;
        }
        .slider .slide:nth-child(2) {
            background: url("/images/slider-2.jpeg") no-repeat center center/cover;
        }
        .slider .slide:nth-child(3) {
            background: url("/images/slider-3.jpeg") no-repeat center center/cover;
        }
        .slider .slide:nth-child(4) {
            background: url("/images/slider-4.jpeg") no-repeat center center/cover;
        }
        .slider .slide:nth-child(5) {
            background: url("/images/slider-5.jpeg") no-repeat center center/cover;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="js-loading">
    <div class="loading">
        <div class="loader">
            <div class="circle"></div>
            <div class="circle"></div>
            <div class="circle"></div>
            <div class="circle"></div>
            <div class="circle"></div>
        </div>
        <h1>Loading</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="slider">
        <div class="slide active">
            <div class="content">
                <p>It's not fun to fail, but it just might be the only way to succeed.</p>
                <p class="blockquote">Jeff Goins</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
            <div class="content">
                <p>Read every book, blog, website, whatever, about what you want to be an expert in.</p>
                <p class="blockquote">James Altucher</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
            <div class="content">
                <p>Never blog just to put something out there. I would post only things that excite me.</p>
                <p class="blockquote">Hanneli Mustaparta</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
            <div class="content">
                <p>No matter what I do, I always come home to my blog.</p>
                <p class="blockquote">Matt Mullenweg</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
            <div class="content">
                <p>When I wrote my first blog, I got one response. Now, I sometimes get as many as 400 responses for my posts.</p>
                <p class="blockquote">Amitabh Bachchan</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="enter">
        <a href="/blogs" class="learn-more">
            <div class="circle">
                <span class="icon arrow"></span>
            </div>
            <p class="button-text">Enter the world of Blogs</p>
        </a>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/slider.js"></script>
</body>
</html>